    "description": "Discipline: Dianxue\nSkill: Medicine Skill TN 8 -1 per Rank of Dianxue\nType: Normal\nQi: 1\n\nYou use your knowledge of the meridian points to boost a person’s vitality. If you Succeed on your Medicine Skill roll (TN 8 -1 per Rank of Dianxue), this allows you raise a person from incapacitated and remove a single Wound provided you can touch their chest with your palm. The target cannot be healed further using this technique without doing so Cathartically. This skill takes ten minutes to perform. Cathartic: You flow your own Qi through the target’s meridian point. Enables you to heal a target you touch by 1 Wound per Rank of Qi you possess.",
